5000,Andean School Of Yoga,https://www.andeanyogaschool.com/,"22 Day 200 Hours Yoga Teacher Training in Pisac, Sacred Valley, Peru","22 Day 200 Hours Yoga Teacher Training in Pisac, Sacred Valley, Peru","Andean School Of Yoga 22 Day 200 Hours Yoga Teacher Training in Pisac, Sacred Valley, Peru ",https://www.andeanyogaschool.com/200hoursytt,Pisac,Yoga,Yoga Teacher Training,22,3800,3100,USD,164,"We start our second week connecting with the teachings of the here and now, exploring the purpose and direction of our lives. We honor our personal experience and the capacity to share it with those we love. We will visit a local community and share the teachings of the Andean Cosmovision, related to the fantastic locals who have kept their traditions with a sense of gratitude and reciprocity.
On the asana portion of the practice, we will study the standing postures, explore vinyasa's nature, and connect our creative power to bring together different poses through dynamic and cohesive sequencing. 
We will study the most relevant yoga literature in the philosophy classes, such as the Bhagavad Gita and The Patanjali Sutras. We will close the week with a spiritual pilgrimage to a sacred site around the area, where we will share a San Pedro Ceremony and put everything you have learned into practice.","Hatha Yoga, Vinyasa Yoga, Yin Yoga, Acro Yoga",,"Nourish Your Body and Soul

Delight in wholesome and flavorful meals, meticulously prepared to fuel your yoga journey and nourish your well-being.

Daily Vegetarian and Vegan Meals:
Indulge in delectable daily meals, crafted with fresh and nutritious ingredients. The menu is predominantly vegetarian, with ample vegan options to cater to diverse dietary preferences. Relish the burst of flavors and the nourishment of mindful eating, enhancing your holistic experience.

A Day of Rest:
Please note that meals will not be served on Sundays, offering you the opportunity to explore the local cuisine and enjoy the vibrant food culture of the region.

At the Andean School of Yoga, they understand the vital role of nourishing food in your holistic journey. Our carefully curated meals aim to provide you with the energy, vitality, and wellness needed to fully immerse in the transformative experience of yoga and self-discovery.

