Personal expenses","Arrival by Airplane:
Opt for a flight landing at Alejandro Velasco Astete International Airport (CUZ). To further ease your journey, the Andean School of Yoga is pleased to organize a taxi pickup for you from the airport. This convenient service is available at a nominal additional charge of 20 USD, ensuring your comfortable and timely arrival at our retreat center.

Let them take care of the logistics as you prepare your mind and spirit for an enriching experience at the Andean School of Yoga. Your peaceful adventure into the world of yoga and self-discovery awaits, and we are here to guide you every step of the way.

Airport: Alejandro Velasco Astete International Airport Airport transfer available: Alejandro Velasco Astete International Airport (Rs. 1,666 per person)
